{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/servicereference"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"article","metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"}],"role":"article","title":"Service Reference","roleHeading":"Article"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/ServiceReference"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"API reference for "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RevenueCatPaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" — the RevenueCat-backed "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" conformer that the paywall plugin consumes."}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Related Documentation","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/MockServiceReference","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/RevenueCatPaywallService"],"anchor":"Related-Documentation"},{"generated":true,"title":"Reference","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/MockServiceReference","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/UIComponentsReference"],"anchor":"Reference"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"code":"RevenueCatPaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" adapts "},{"code":"RevenueCat.Purchases","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to the "},{"code":"PaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol that "},{"code":"SwiduxPaywall.PaywallPlugin","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" requires. It does one job: translate "},{"code":"CustomerInfo","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" into "},{"code":"EntitlementSnapshot","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" (defined by "},{"code":"SwiduxPaywall","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") so the plugin can drive its state. Configuration of the RevenueCat SDK itself remains the caller’s responsibility."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For a step-by-step integration walkthrough, see ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService"},{"text":". For the entitlement-mapping rules, see ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Library target","anchor":"Library-target"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Product: ","type":"text"},{"code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","type":"codeVoice"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Import: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"import SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Package.swift"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":[".product(name: \"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\", package: \"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\"),"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Types","anchor":"Types"},{"level":3,"text":"``doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/RevenueCatPaywallService``","type":"heading","anchor":"docSwiduxRevenueCatPaywalldocumentationSwiduxRevenueCatPaywallRevenueCatPaywallService"},{"code":["public struct RevenueCatPaywallService: PaywallService {","    public init(","        entitlementID: String,","        permanentLicenseEntitlementID: String? = nil","    )","","    public func customerInfo() async throws -> EntitlementSnapshot","    public func customerInfoStream() -> AsyncStream<EntitlementSnapshot>","    public func restorePurchases() async throws -> EntitlementSnapshot","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Value type. Holds two ","type":"text"},{"code":"String","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" identifiers and forwards every call to "},{"code":"Purchases.shared","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". Safe to construct freely; cheap to pass into "},{"code":"PaywallPlugin","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"level":4,"text":"Initializer","type":"heading","anchor":"Initializer"},{"code":["public init(","    entitlementID: String,","    permanentLicenseEntitlementID: String? = nil",")"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"entitlementID","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" — RevenueCat entitlement identifier that grants pro access. Surfaces as ","type":"text"},{"code":"EntitlementSnapshot.isPro","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" when active.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"permanentLicenseEntitlementID","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" — Optional secondary identifier for a lifetime \/ permanent entitlement. Surfaces as ","type":"text"},{"code":"EntitlementSnapshot.hasPermanentLicense","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" when active. Pass ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" if the app has no separate lifetime SKU."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"name":"Important","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Call "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/RevenueCatPaywall\/configure(apiKey:appUserID:userDefaults:logLevel:)","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" before constructing the service. The service does not configure RevenueCat itself, and ","type":"text"},{"code":"Purchases.shared","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" traps if used unconfigured.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"important","type":"aside"},{"text":"`customerInfo() async throws -> EntitlementSnapshot`","level":4,"anchor":"customerInfo-async-throws-%3E-EntitlementSnapshot","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"One-shot fetch. Calls ","type":"text"},{"code":"Purchases.shared.customerInfo()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and maps the result.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Throws whatever the RevenueCat SDK throws (","type":"text"},{"code":"ErrorCode.networkError","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":".offlineConnectionError","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", etc.). The plugin catches the error and dispatches ","type":"text"},{"code":".refreshFailed(message)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"text":"`customerInfoStream() -> AsyncStream<EntitlementSnapshot>`","level":4,"anchor":"customerInfoStream-%3E-AsyncStream%3CEntitlementSnapshot%3E","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Long-lived stream. Wraps ","type":"text"},{"code":"Purchases.shared.customerInfoStream","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and yields a new ","type":"text"},{"code":"EntitlementSnapshot","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" for every change RevenueCat reports — purchase, refund, family-share update, sandbox renewal.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The stream finishes when the underlying RevenueCat stream finishes. The plugin’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".observeCustomerInfo"},{"type":"text","text":" effect normally keeps it alive for the duration of the session; cancel by cancelling the consuming "},{"code":"Task","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", which terminates the stream and tears down the bridge."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"`restorePurchases() async throws -> EntitlementSnapshot`","anchor":"restorePurchases-async-throws-%3E-EntitlementSnapshot","level":4,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Calls "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Purchases.shared.restorePurchases()"},{"type":"text","text":" and maps the result. Throws whatever the SDK throws on error."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The plugin’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".restorePurchases"},{"text":" action wraps this call and dispatches ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".customerInfoUpdated"},{"text":" on success or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".refreshFailed"},{"text":" on error.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Entitlement mapping","anchor":"Entitlement-mapping","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For every "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomerInfo"},{"type":"text","text":" the service receives:"}]},{"header":"row","type":"table","rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Configuration"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isPro"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"hasPermanentLicense"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"entitlementID","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" active"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"(next column)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"entitlementID","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" inactive or missing","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"false","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"(next column)","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"permanentLicenseEntitlementID == nil"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"—"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"permanentLicenseEntitlementID","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" active","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"—","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"permanentLicenseEntitlementID"},{"type":"text","text":" inactive or missing"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"—"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"false","type":"codeVoice"}]}]]]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Both flags are checked independently against the same "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomerInfo"},{"type":"text","text":". A user with both active subscription and lifetime entitlements gets both flags set. See "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" for the reasoning behind the truth table."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"references":{"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/UIComponentsReference":{"url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/uicomponentsreference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/UIComponentsReference","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"API reference for the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"revenueCatPaywall"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"revenueCatCustomerCenter"},{"type":"text","text":" view modifiers — the SwiftUI surface of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"kind":"article","role":"article","type":"topic","title":"UI Components Reference"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRev